@startuml
title 4. Merge & Cleanup
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor Student as S
participant "GitWizard" as W
participant "GitHub CLI" as GH
participant "Git" as G
participant "GitHub" as R

S -> W : Select option 4

== Step 1: List open PRs ==

W -> GH : gh pr list
GH -> R : GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls
R --> GH : Open PRs
GH --> W : "#35 Implement edit community... feature/BR-02-..."
W -> S : Display PR list
S -> W : PR number: 35

== Step 2: Check PR status ==

W -> GH : gh pr view 35 --json\nstate,reviewDecision,statusCheckRollup
GH -> R : GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/35
R --> GH : PR details
GH --> W : State: OPEN | Review: APPROVED | CI: SUCCESS
W -> S : "State: OPEN | Review: APPROVED | CI: SUCCESS"

== Step 3: Merge ==

W -> S : "Merge PR #35? (y/n)"
S -> W : y
W -> GH : gh pr merge 35\n--merge --delete-branch
GH -> R : PUT /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/35/merge
R -> R : Merge commit created
R -> R : Delete remote branch
R --> GH : Merged successfully
GH --> W : Merged + branch deleted

== Step 4: Local cleanup ==

W -> G : git checkout main
G --> W : Switched to main
W -> G : git pull origin main
G -> R : Fetch merge commit
R --> G : Fast-forward
G --> W : Updated to latest
W -> G : git branch -d\nfeature/BR-02-edit-existing-community
G --> W : Local branch deleted

W -> S : "PR #35 merged!\nYour feature is on main."

note right of S
  The feature branch is gone
  (both remote and local).
  main now contains the work.
  Ready for the next feature
  (option 1) or release tag
  (option 5).
end note
@enduml
